title: SC EP:774 I Hit It With My Car
itunes:title: SC EP:774 I Hit It With My Car
description: Doug writes "The reason I am emailing you is because a few months ago here in Arkansas I was driving down a two-lane highway just after dark when something that I could have swore was a orangutan with reddish hair came hauling ass up onto the highway from out of the woods and it had a raccoon hanging out of his mouth."
